messages.message: Hi, i was working with notebooks in dogfood and not prod

Are you facing issues in dogfood or prod or both?

Prod - not able to open the notebook
dogfood - not able to install the packages
the dogfood change is due to my testing, not sure about prodâ€™s reason, i did not change anything in prod.
Regarding prod, if you pushed any changes to webapp, you might wanna look into dynamic proxy logs and restart the pods.

The problem lies with dynamic proxy and it has started to come up on and off after a few of the third party packages were upgraded to remove security vulnerabilities back in July. We don't quite know yet why this problem occurs. I have rolled back to a dynamic proxy version prior to these third party package upgrades in prod.
